OL,3,CSouth West Water CEO Susan davy to
OL,4,Cretire after nearly five years
OL,6,FSouth West Water Chief Executive
OL,7,FOfficer Susan Davy will step down from
OL,8,Fher role and retire from Pennon
OL,9,FGroup's board, bringing an end to her
OL,10,F18-year career with the water utility
OL,11,Fgiant.
OL,13,FMs Davy has been CEO of Pennon Group,
OL,14,Fthe parent company of South West
OL,15,FWater, since July 2020. Before that,
OL,16,Fshe served as Chief Financial Officer
OL,17,Ffor five years.
