OL,3,CSouth West Water CEO Susan davy to
OL,4,Cretire after nearly five years
OL,6,FIn a statement, she said that "the
OL,7,Ftime was right to pass leadership to a
OL,8,Fnew generation" after nearly three
OL,9,Fdecades in the water sector.
OL,11,FHer retirement comes just a day after
OL,12,Findustry regulator Ofwat found a
OL,13,F"range of failures" in how South West
OL,14,FWater had managed its wastewater
OL,15,Ftreatment works and sewer network.
