OL,3,CSouth West Water CEO Susan davy to
OL,4,Cretire after nearly five years
OL,6,FOfwat said South West Water (SWW)
OL,7,F"failed to meet its legal
OL,8,Fobligations", pointing to a lack of
OL,9,Fadequate management systems, including
OL,10,Foversight from the senior leaders and
OL,11,Fboard.
OL,13,FLynn Parker, Ofwat's Senior Director
OL,14,Fof Enforcement, said: "We've found
OL,15,Fsignificant failings that have led to
OL,16,Fmore spills than the law allows over a
OL,17,Fsignificant number of years so we
OL,18,Fconsider this to be systemic failings.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
