OL,3,CSouth West Water CEO Susan davy to
OL,4,Cretire after nearly five years
OL,6,FSWW has proposed spending #24 million
OL,7,Funder an "enforcement package" to
OL,8,Ftarget storm overflows, tackle sewer
OL,9,Fmisuse, and provide funding for
OL,10,Fenvironmental groups.
OL,12,FThis will be funded by the company and
OL,13,Fshareholders.
OL,15,FAs a result, it has avoided being
OL,16,Ffined by Ofwat which would have been
OL,17,Fthe lesser amount of #19 million -
OL,18,F6.5% of its annual turnover - going
OL,19,Fback to the Treasury.
