OL,3,CSouth West Water CEO Susan davy to
OL,4,Cretire after nearly five years
OL,6,FThis investigation is part of work by
OL,7,FOfwat and the Environment Agency to
OL,8,Freview all water and wastewater
OL,9,Fcompanies in England and Wales.
OL,11,FReflecting on her decision to retire,
OL,12,FMs Davy said: "It has been an honour
OL,13,Fto serve as Chief Executive Officer of
OL,14,FPennon. Running a water company is
OL,15,Falways interesting, often challenging,
OL,16,Fbut totally fulfilling.
OL,18,F"I have enjoyed taking responsibility
OL,19,Ffor the provision of a sustainable
OL,20,Fservice to millions of homes."
