OL,4,Cretire after nearly five years
OL,6,FMs Davy highlighted that Ofwat's
OL,7,Frecent approval of the company's
OL,8,Finvestment plans provided "a natural
OL,9,Fjuncture" to retire from Pennon.
OL,11,FShe added "This has been my life for
OL,12,Fthe past 30 years, and now it's right
OL,13,FI hand this huge responsibility to the
OL,14,Fnext generation of leaders."
OL,16,FMs Davy's successor will be announced
OL,17,Fin due course.
