OL,4,Cretire after nearly five years
OL,6,FWhat is South West Water doing to
OL,7,Faddress the issues?
OL,9,FSouth West Water has taken already
OL,10,Ftaken some steps to address its
OL,11,Fcompliance issues.
OL,13,FIt says it has invested more than #16
OL,14,Fmillion to remedy the 21 WWTW that
OL,15,Ffailed to meet requirements.
OL,17,FIt is in the process of delivering a
OL,18,Fstorm overflow reduction plan
OL,19,Finvesting to reduce spills and greater
OL,20,Foversight of its compliance with
OL,21,Fenvironmental obligations.
