OL,3,CSouth West Water CEO Susan davy to
OL,4,Cretire after nearly five years
OL,6,FNoah Law, MP for St Austell and
OL,7,FNewquay, has had the company's CEO
OL,8,FSusan Davy on 'resignation watch' for
OL,9,Fsome time.
OL,11,FHe said: "I think they have a long
OL,12,Fstanding plan in place for different
OL,13,Fasset management periods but what I
OL,14,Fwant them to do now is accelerate that
OL,15,Fpace and show they know the sense of
OL,16,Furgency residents have around this.
OL,18,F"I would urge a real caution of Susan
OL,19,FDavy as to whether she looks at taking
OL,20,Fher bonus this year after all of this
OL,21,Fnews.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/11
