OL,3,CSouth West Water CEO Susan davy to
OL,4,Cretire after nearly five years
OL,6,FWhen asked if Davy should resign,
OL,7,FLouise Rowe, SWW's Director of
OL,8,FCompliance, said: "Susan became CEO in
OL,9,F2020. Under her leadership SWW has
OL,10,Fsignificantly upheld the governance,
OL,11,Fwe've put hundreds of millions of
OL,12,Fpounds into the wastewater activities
OL,13,Fand all of that has been recognised by
OL,14,FOfwat in their report that
OL,15,Fimprovements have happened."
OL,17,F"We will continue to make the
OL,18,Fimprovements needed where wastewater
OL,19,Factivity needs it across our beautiful
OL,20,Fregion."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/11
