OL,4,Cretire after nearly five years
OL,6,FWhat has the reaction been?
OL,8,FIn a statement, South Devon's MP
OL,9,FCaroline Voaden said "this decision
OL,10,Fshould have come a lot sooner".
OL,12,FShe said "Today's announcement closes
OL,13,Fa sorry tenure as CEO of South West
OL,14,FWater where Ms. Davy oversaw shocking
OL,15,Flevels of sewage spills, plummeting
OL,16,Fcustomer confidence, and a water
OL,17,Fcontamination event that sent people
OL,18,Fto hospital.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/11
