OL,3,CSouth West Water CEO Susan davy to
OL,4,Cretire after nearly five years
OL,6,F"In truth, this decision should have
OL,7,Fcome a lot sooner. The shocking report
OL,8,Ffrom Ofwat was clearly the straw that
OL,9,Fbroke the camel's back, and for me,
OL,10,Fepitomised the negligent attitude SWW
OL,11,Fhas shown to the environment and its
OL,12,Fcustomers in the past five years.
OL,14,F"I look forward to meeting the new CEO
OL,15,Fof SWW when they are announced, and I
OL,16,Fhope they can learn from the
OL,17,Fsystematic mistakes Ms Davy made
OL,18,Fthroughout her time in post."
